Status |\n|--------|--------|:------:|\n| **OBO token not forwarded** | All authenticated Flowise operations fail | ❌ Open — P0 |\n| **Flowise gateway unhealthy** | `get_framework_status` confirms endpoint down | ❌ Open — P0 |\n| **Health check false positive** | `flowise_health_check` says healthy while API is down | ⚠️ Open — P1 |\n\nUntil the P0 token-forwarding defect is resolved, no Flowise workflow can be created, listed, validated against the live store, or analyzed. The structural pre-save validator is the only Flowise tool currently functional for authenticated users.","timestamp":"2026-02-21T00:36:31.616Z","mcpCalls":[{"id":"toolu_bdrk_01SHjvmtN51EoVkrj5Hz6aRP","name":"flowise_validate_flow","tool":"flowise_validate_flow","toolName":"flowise_validate_flow","serverId":"openagentic_flowise","serverName":"openagentic_flowise","executedOn":"mcp-proxy","arguments":{"userId":"user","flowData":"{\n  \"nodes\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"chatOpenAgentic_0\",\n      \"position\": {\"x\": 100, \"y\": 200},\n      \"type\": \"customNode\",\n      \"data\": {\n        \"id\": \"chatOpenAgentic_0\",\n        \"label\": \"OpenAgentic Chat\",\n        \"name\": \"chatOpenAgentic\",\n        \"type\": \"ChatModel\",\n        \"baseClasses\": [\"BaseChatModel\", \"BaseLanguageModel\"],\n        \"inputs\": {\n          \"modelName\": \"gemini-2.0-flash-001\",\n          \"temperature\": 0.7\n        }\n      },\n      \"width\": 300,\n      \"height\": 150\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"promptTemplate_0\",\n      \"position\": {\"x\": 100, \"y\": 450},\n      \"type\": \"customNode\",\n      \"data\": {\n        \"id\": \"promptTemplate_0\",\n        \"label\": \"Prompt Template\",\n        \"name\": \"promptTemplate\",\n        \"type\": \"PromptTemplate\",\n        \"baseClasses\": [\"PromptTemplate\", \"BaseStringPromptTemplate\"],\n        \"inputs\": {\n          \"template\": \"You are a helpful assistant. Answer the following question:\\n{question}\",\n          \"i